OL,3,CHow you could apply to spend a year
OL,4,Cworking and living in Italy
OL,6,Fhas long been a favoured holiday
OL,7,Fdestination for Britons with its world
OL,8,Ffamous culture, cuisine and landscapes
OL,9,Foffering a variety of idyllic getaways.
OL,11,FBut for most a getaway is exactly how
OL,12,Fit stays. A piece of paradise that
OL,13,Flasts for a handful of days at a time.
OL,15,FWell, what if that holiday didn't have
OL,16,Fto end so quickly? Italy has now
OL,17,Fbecome the latest European Union (EU)
OL,18,Fcountry to introduce a so-called
OL,19,F'digital nomad' visa.
