OL,3,CHow you could apply to spend a year
OL,4,Cworking and living in Italy
OL,6,FAs a result, Britons who work from
OL,7,Fhome can now apply to live in Italy
OL,8,Ffor up to a year.
OL,10,FSo, how exactly does the scheme work?
OL,11,FITV News explains.
OL,13,FWhat is a digital nomad visa?
OL,15,FItaly's government approved a law
OL,16,Fintroducing digital nomad visas in
OL,17,FMarch 2022, but the regulations for
OL,18,Fsuch a permit were only issued at the
OL,19,Fstart of April.
