OL,3,CHow you could apply to spend a year
OL,4,Cworking and living in Italy
OL,6,FThe visa is meant for freelancers,
OL,7,Fself-employed digital nomads and
OL,8,Fremote employees on a company payroll
OL,9,Ffrom non-EU countries, according to
OL,10,Fthe international Italian law firm .
OL,12,FHow long does it last for?
OL,14,FA digital nomad visa grants a
OL,15,Fsuccessful applicant up to a year's
OL,16,Fstay in Italy, but once there you can
OL,17,Fapply to renew your immigration permit.
