OL,3,CHow you could apply to spend a year
OL,4,Cworking and living in Italy
OL,6,FAnyone interested in applying for a
OL,7,Fdigital nomad visa must do so through
OL,8,Fthe relevant Italian Consulate in
OL,9,Ftheir existing country of residence.
OL,11,FThe United Kingdom is subdivided into
OL,12,Fthree consular districts, which fall
OL,13,Funder the jurisdiction of the
OL,14,FConsulate General of Italy in London,
OL,15,Fthe Consulate of Italy in Manchester
OL,16,Fand the Consulate General in Edinburgh.
